Smart Medication Reminder

Interface an OLED display and a buzzer to remind patients when to take medicine, using a real-time clock module and VSDSQUADRON Mini risc v board. 

Project Overview
This system will:
Display medicine reminder messages on an OLED screen.
Use a buzzer to alert the patient at scheduled times.
Store and retrieve the schedule from an RTC (Real-Time Clock) module.

Components Required
RISC-V board
OLED Display 
RTC Module 
Buzzer
Push Button 
